metadata.title: Bell 47
aws::graph::propositions: # Surviving Bell 47 Aircraft by Country
Austria has a Bell 47 G-3B-1T with registration OE-XDM.
Bell 47 G-3B-1T with registration OE-XDM is a former United States Army TH-13T.
Bell 47 G-3B-1T with registration OE-XDM is airworthy.
Bell 47 G-3B-1T with registration OE-XDM is operated by The Flying Bulls.
The Flying Bulls are located in Salzburg.
Australia has a Bell 47 G with registration A1-402.
Bell 47 G with registration A1-402 is a former Australian Army aircraft.
Bell 47 G with registration A1-402 was operated by 161 Independent Recce Flight.
Bell 47 G with registration A1-402 is on static display.
Bell 47 G with registration A1-402 is displayed at HARS Parkes Aviation Museum.
United States has a Bell 47G-2 with registration N2490B.
Bell 47G-2 with registration N2490B is airworthy.
Bell 47G-2 with registration N2490B is at the EAA AirVenture Museum.
EAA AirVenture Museum is located in Oshkosh, Wisconsin.
United States has a Bell 47G-2A with registration N7576.
Bell 47G-2A with registration N7576 is airworthy.
Bell 47G-2A with registration N7576 is at the Classic Rotors Museum.
Classic Rotors Museum is located in Ramona, California.
United States has a Continental Copters Bell 47G with registration N6356X.
Continental Copters Bell 47G with registration N6356X is airworthy.
Continental Copters Bell 47G with registration N6356X is at the Mid America Flight Museum.
Mid America Flight Museum is located in Mount Pleasant, Texas.

text:
## Surviving aircraft

Austria
OE-XDM  Bell 47 G-3B-1T (a former United States Army TH-13T) airworthy with The Flying Bulls in Salzburg.
Australia
A1-402  - Bell 47 G former Australian Army 161 Independent Recce Flight on static display at HARS Parkes Aviation Museum
United States
N2490B  Bell 47G-2 airworthy at the EAA AirVenture Museum in Oshkosh, Wisconsin.
N7576  Bell 47G-2A airworthy at the Classic Rotors Museum in Ramona, California.
N6356X  Continental Copters Bell 47G airworthy at the Mid America Flight Museum in Mount Pleasant, Texas.
